 class="field-content"><h1 class="title">The day is made</h1><div class="description">Imposing and impressive, the elegant five-star Sugar Beach unfurls along the sun-drenched, sheltered bay of Flic-en-Flac, bordered by crystalline waters, manicured gardens and one of the most picturesque beaches on the island. This plantation-style resort masterfully balances old-world opulence with modern comforts and offers panoramic views of the sunset over the ocean. A testament to the aesthetics of colonial estates in a bygone era, Sugar Beach Mauritius today provides a luxurious sanctuary for families and couples seeking the ultimate holiday in paradise.</div><div class="read-more"><a href="https://www.sugarbeachresort.com/en/rooms-suites">Read more</a></div> </span></div></div></div></div></div> </section><section class="views-element-container block block-views block-views-blocktimeless-memories-block-1 clearfix" id="block-sugarbeach-views-block-timeless-memories-block-1"><div class="form-group"><div class="view view-timeless-memories view-id-timeless_memories view-display-id-block_1 js-view-dom-id-44684500affcd8064d21ffbff1c0d6629331af37867373771e05797a5bebaebd"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row"><div class="timeless-memories-list-wrapper"><div class="timeless-memories-list"><div class="col-1 wow slideInLeft" data-wow-duration="1s"><div class="grid-item carre_petit"><div class="item-list"><div class="item-title">Sun Memory Lab</div> <img src="/themes/sunresorts/images/loading.gif" width="240" height="240" alt="Sun Memory Lab" class="lazyload img-responsive" data-src="https://www.sugarbeachresort.com/sites/default/files/styles/max_240x240_/public/externals/Ambre_SUN_Memory_Lab_12-1599x1066-30e49676-9948-4feb-8eb6-dad909f27ef3.jpg?itok=siSDlL0L" typeof="foaf:Image" /><div class="outline-wrapper"> <a href="https://www.sugarbeachresort.com/en/timeless-memories/sun-memory-lab"> Sun Memory Lab <span class="draw"></span> </a></div></div></div><div class="grid-item c